Klasse RewardApplyEvent

java.lang.Object
org.bukkit.event.Event
net.jandie1505.playerlevels.core.events.RewardApplyEvent
Alle implementierten Schnittstellen:
org.bukkit.event.Cancellable
public class RewardApplyEvent extends org.bukkit.event.Event implements org.bukkit.event.Cancellable
This event is fired when a reward is applied.
The result of this event will control if the event is applied and/or marked as applied.
